casebody.data:
No. 942,

Misc.

Chessman v. Dickson, Warden. George T. Davis, Rosalie S. Asher and A. L. Wirin for petitioner. Stanley Mosk, Attorney General of California, and Arlo E. Smith, Deputy Attorney General, for respondent.

The application for stay of execution presented to Mr. Justice Douglas and by him referred to the Court is denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of California denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
